  textVersion  =
  paste("Haslett, J., & Parnell, A.C. (2008). A simple monotone process with application to radiocarbon‚Äêdated depth chronologies. Journal of the Royal Statistical Society: Series C (Applied Statistics), 57(4), 399-418.")
